abstract: According to the former head of Intel’s server chip business, Itanium has finally moved into the black.
snippet: According to the former head of Intel’s server chip business, Itanium has finally moved into the black.
lead_paragraph: Intel’s much-maligned and often ridiculed Itanium chip has finally started paying for itself.

headline.main: A Decade Later, Intel’s Itanium Chip Makes a Profit
